Summary: Rapid erratic movement of diamond shaped object
divs: Sighting DetailsWent outside saw bright star, but object moved latterally and began to get closer and then further away for the duration of 1.5 hours. Object diamond shaped and organge and green. Live very close to ARMY AVIATION HQ with many AHP's for many years. Never seen object do these movements before, I am certain that this movement could not be flares. I have numerous videos to document.
